WEBVTT

00:00:00.175 --> 00:00:02.121
[Production supported by the
Ministry of Culture, Sports and Tourism]

00:00:02.145 --> 00:00:03.097
[This drama is fictional.]

00:00:03.122 --> 00:00:04.073
[Child and animal scenes complied
with broadcast guidelines.]

00:00:04.247 --> 00:00:08.152
[Neulsarang Bookstore]

00:00:26.945 --> 00:00:27.577
Dad!

00:00:27.578 --> 00:00:28.861
You scared me!

00:00:29.931 --> 00:00:31.361
What are you doing?

00:00:32.331 --> 00:00:34.198
Didn't you go to school?

00:00:34.391 --> 00:00:36.402
What are you going to do if you're late?

00:00:36.556 --> 00:00:39.137
I still have plenty of time
before I'm late.

00:00:40.285 --> 00:00:42.241
Oh? You're right.

00:00:43.841 --> 00:00:46.041
Dad, you smoked again, didn't you?

00:00:47.071 --> 00:00:49.257
Who did you get that keen nose from?

00:00:49.282 --> 00:00:51.053
Seriously, Dad.

00:00:51.661 --> 00:00:54.823
You always smoke
but forget this every time.

00:01:00.862 --> 00:01:04.889
Okay, after lunch, you need to
take this and this, and in the evening...

00:01:04.890 --> 00:01:05.932
Yeah, yeah.

00:01:05.956 --> 00:01:09.331
Thanks to my daughter,
I'll live to be 100.

00:01:09.913 --> 00:01:10.673
Right?

00:01:10.697 --> 00:01:13.366
What would you do
without a daughter like me?

00:01:13.566 --> 00:01:16.731
To live happily
with my daughter,

00:01:16.755 --> 00:01:18.661
I should take my meds properly.

00:01:19.061 --> 00:01:21.301
I'll check if you took your meds tonight.

00:01:21.942 --> 00:01:22.942
By the way.

00:01:23.330 --> 00:01:24.822
You remember what's
happening tonight, right?

00:01:24.846 --> 00:01:25.711
Of course!

00:01:25.712 --> 00:01:27.906
Hey, you'll be late
for school. Hurry up.

00:01:27.971 --> 00:01:28.986
I'm off to school!

00:01:29.011 --> 00:01:30.259
Hey, you didn't forget anything, right?

00:01:30.284 --> 00:01:31.284
Nope!

00:01:32.091 --> 00:01:33.771
[Fiction writing class]

00:01:34.702 --> 00:01:37.732
I think it's better to delete
this paragraph before publishing.

00:01:38.416 --> 00:01:39.846
But why?

00:01:39.871 --> 00:01:44.251
It feels like we're forcing the ending
on the readers, and I don't like that.

00:01:45.396 --> 00:01:46.941
Instead,

00:01:47.782 --> 00:01:50.781
can we publish a single
copy that includes it?

00:01:51.051 --> 00:01:53.521
There's someone I want to
give a special gift to.

00:01:54.311 --> 00:01:55.551
I'm not sure.

00:01:55.651 --> 00:01:57.331
That might be difficult.

00:02:02.061 --> 00:02:03.710
Alright.

00:02:03.711 --> 00:02:05.121
I'll ask the publisher about it.

00:02:05.496 --> 00:02:06.848
Thank you.

00:02:06.873 --> 00:02:09.328
Oh, please, I'm counting
on you, Writer Yang.

00:02:09.353 --> 00:02:11.501
No way. Me? A writer?

00:02:11.502 --> 00:02:13.131
But you are an writer, right?

00:02:14.334 --> 00:02:15.451
Thank you.

00:02:25.017 --> 00:02:28.597
Happy birthday.

00:02:28.781 --> 00:02:33.160
Dear teacher.

00:02:33.260 --> 00:02:36.551
Happy birthday.

00:02:36.590 --> 00:02:37.784
Woo!

00:02:37.809 --> 00:02:39.364
- Blow out the candles.
- Thank you.

00:02:39.868 --> 00:02:41.487
Wow!

00:02:53.578 --> 00:02:54.578
[Yeon Woo]

00:02:54.611 --> 00:02:55.611
[Kim Hyun Jin]

00:03:01.997 --> 00:03:02.997
[Cho Yun Seo]

00:03:03.022 --> 00:03:04.155
[Choi Byung Chan]

00:03:06.825 --> 00:03:08.774
[Im Ji Eun]

00:03:18.006 --> 00:03:20.708
LOVE PHOBIA

00:03:28.485 --> 00:03:29.885
My beautiful daughter.

00:03:30.491 --> 00:03:31.908
My beautiful daughter.

00:03:35.421 --> 00:03:36.399
Mom...

00:03:36.423 --> 00:03:39.068
Mom, mom, please!

00:03:43.525 --> 00:03:44.831
Who are you people?

00:03:46.285 --> 00:03:47.664
Where's my daughter?

00:03:49.375 --> 00:03:50.631
Where's my daughter?

00:03:51.571 --> 00:03:52.512
My daughter!

00:03:52.536 --> 00:03:53.835
Where's my daughter?

00:03:54.918 --> 00:03:56.050
Bia!

00:03:56.786 --> 00:03:58.687
Bia, Bia!

00:04:02.491 --> 00:04:03.781
Please take care of Bia.

00:04:10.342 --> 00:04:11.611
Bia, please come inside...

00:04:12.011 --> 00:04:13.011
Let go of me.

00:04:16.441 --> 00:04:17.441
Please...

00:04:19.675 --> 00:04:20.879
Please...

00:04:21.973 --> 00:04:23.791
Please, please...

00:04:33.837 --> 00:04:34.698
[Kim Jina. Dolbom Nursing Home]

00:04:34.722 --> 00:04:35.788
So,

00:04:37.888 --> 00:04:40.131
you brought her here to threaten us?

00:04:40.681 --> 00:04:42.131
I'm sorry.

00:04:42.381 --> 00:04:43.680
Are you out of your mind?

00:04:43.870 --> 00:04:44.968
Even so,

00:04:45.245 --> 00:04:47.335
please fix the
server issue quickly.

00:04:47.772 --> 00:04:48.503
Please?

00:04:49.225 --> 00:04:52.921
Without my darling, life is meaningless.

00:04:53.171 --> 00:04:55.103
There's talk about
some dummy issue causing

00:04:55.128 --> 00:04:57.981
'It's You' to go bankrupt
and shut down services.

00:04:59.351 --> 00:05:00.401
That's not true, right?

00:05:02.001 --> 00:05:04.711
I've spent so much money on my darling!

00:05:13.260 --> 00:05:14.233
Are you sure...

00:05:15.963 --> 00:05:17.996
that she's Yun Bia's mother?

00:05:19.079 --> 00:05:20.079
Actually?

00:05:26.006 --> 00:05:28.501
We're just getting
a handle on the situation.

00:05:28.831 --> 00:05:31.577
We'll make sure to take action
against the employee.

00:05:32.078 --> 00:05:33.388
We're really sorry.

00:05:50.534 --> 00:05:53.525
I'll take your Mom to the nursing home.

00:05:53.526 --> 00:05:54.851
Let's talk later.

00:05:55.241 --> 00:05:56.771
You go home for now.

00:06:07.218 --> 00:06:08.337
What happened here?

00:06:08.361 --> 00:06:09.292
Let's go.

00:06:11.128 --> 00:06:12.301
I'll go to the nursing home with you.

00:06:16.826 --> 00:06:18.171
Don't worry about it.

00:06:18.878 --> 00:06:20.696
Unless you want to make Bia suffer more.

00:06:21.201 --> 00:06:22.043
What?

00:06:22.732 --> 00:06:24.631
Whose fault do you think this is?

00:06:51.555 --> 00:06:55.625
Dear teacher.

00:06:55.725 --> 00:06:59.191
Happy birthday.

00:06:59.216 --> 00:07:00.211
Woo!

00:07:00.247 --> 00:07:01.814
- Blow out the candles.
- Thank you.

00:07:02.244 --> 00:07:04.008
Wow!

00:07:18.227 --> 00:07:19.429
What's wrong with you?

00:07:20.701 --> 00:07:21.811
Why did you do it?

00:07:25.036 --> 00:07:26.521
Why did you do it?

00:07:36.571 --> 00:07:37.962
Are you doing okay?

00:07:37.987 --> 00:07:39.561
Let me know if you need anything.

00:07:39.611 --> 00:07:40.981
I'll help with anything.

00:07:41.466 --> 00:07:43.702
Those who take
don't understand...

00:07:44.713 --> 00:07:46.021
the sadness of losing.

00:07:50.427 --> 00:07:51.427
Right?

00:07:57.562 --> 00:07:59.658
[One week later]

00:08:04.137 --> 00:08:07.331
Amidst the Dummy Syndrome controversy.

00:08:07.355 --> 00:08:10.781
'It's You' has yet to release
an official statement.

00:08:10.805 --> 00:08:14.794
Some insiders say they need time

00:08:14.819 --> 00:08:17.206
to assess the situation.

00:08:17.496 --> 00:08:20.154
With the successful launch
of 'ForMe Version 2',

00:08:20.155 --> 00:08:24.410
It's You's stock price was rising.
It is currently plummeting.

00:08:24.411 --> 00:08:25.640
At the general shareholders meeting,

00:08:25.641 --> 00:08:29.374
Yun Bia will be held responsible.

00:08:29.751 --> 00:08:30.567
Meanwhile,

00:08:30.568 --> 00:08:33.904
the main model for
'ForMe Version 2', Han Sunho,

00:08:33.905 --> 00:08:37.658
is also not free from the direct
and indirect impacts of this situation.

00:08:37.683 --> 00:08:41.211
Is there any point in us
going to the office now?

00:08:42.264 --> 00:08:44.006
Still, it's better to gather

00:08:44.030 --> 00:08:46.336
and come up with some plans
rather than doing nothing...

00:08:46.636 --> 00:08:48.382
Those darn plans, plans, plans!

00:08:48.402 --> 00:08:50.690
Aren't the Directors being too much?

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:52.925
Why are they kicking out the writers?

00:08:52.926 --> 00:08:54.153
What did they do wrong?

00:08:54.178 --> 00:08:55.758
Calm down, Yukyung.

00:08:55.759 --> 00:08:58.527
They're probably trying to protect
the writers from the fallout.

00:08:59.212 --> 00:09:00.637
Protect them from what?

00:09:00.662 --> 00:09:03.592
Why does Director Yun's attendance
have to be a secret?

00:09:03.616 --> 00:09:05.966
I should at least contact Jiyoung.

00:09:06.411 --> 00:09:08.670
Didn't Director Sul tell us
not to contact anyone?

00:09:08.671 --> 00:09:09.968
Let's just wait for now.

00:09:16.661 --> 00:09:18.002
Yukyung!

00:09:33.316 --> 00:09:34.717
You skipped a meal again?

00:09:35.829 --> 00:09:37.751
When's our shareholders' meeting?

00:09:38.971 --> 00:09:40.300
It's in a week.

00:09:40.896 --> 00:09:42.580
In a week...

00:09:43.402 --> 00:09:44.501
How much has the company lost?

00:09:45.493 --> 00:09:46.493
Bia.

00:09:47.087 --> 00:09:49.141
I'm also working on fixing things, so

00:09:49.631 --> 00:09:51.241
just eat something first...

00:09:57.131 --> 00:09:58.991
Yun Bia, are you going
to crumble like this?

00:09:59.761 --> 00:10:01.486
We can start over!

00:10:01.511 --> 00:10:02.469
Shareholders?

00:10:03.175 --> 00:10:05.811
It's our company, so who can kick us out?

00:10:09.061 --> 00:10:10.036
Have we...

00:10:11.571 --> 00:10:13.081
changed a bit?

00:10:17.364 --> 00:10:18.364
Why?

00:10:19.227 --> 00:10:20.805
Something feels different about us.

00:10:21.100 --> 00:10:22.192
Just...

00:10:23.192 --> 00:10:25.403
It's been a while since we laughed.

00:10:33.740 --> 00:10:35.205
You've got me!

00:10:35.841 --> 00:10:37.311
Everything will be fine.

00:10:38.021 --> 00:10:40.782
You've got that,
and you've got me.

00:10:41.153 --> 00:10:42.493
So what's there to worry about?

00:10:43.031 --> 00:10:45.502
Then and now,

00:10:46.561 --> 00:10:48.392
we can start over.

00:10:50.102 --> 00:10:51.102
Right?

00:10:53.431 --> 00:10:55.487
I admit, you haven't changed.

00:10:55.987 --> 00:10:57.126
You're just the same as before.

00:10:57.570 --> 00:10:58.557
That's a compliment, right?

00:11:03.417 --> 00:11:04.506
Jaehee.

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:08.326
I feel like...

00:11:08.718 --> 00:11:11.008
I haven't properly apologized yet.

00:11:12.945 --> 00:11:14.579
For not telling you...

00:11:15.513 --> 00:11:16.353
about my mom earlier...

00:11:16.378 --> 00:11:17.325
I don't know, I don't know.

00:11:17.350 --> 00:11:18.568
I don't want to hear it.

00:11:21.758 --> 00:11:24.856
You must have had
your reasons, I guess...

00:11:25.621 --> 00:11:27.340
for not telling me
about your mom.

00:11:27.851 --> 00:11:28.851
It's fine.

00:11:30.011 --> 00:11:32.665
Your mom is doing well, so

00:11:35.131 --> 00:11:36.786
take care of yourself first.

00:11:36.911 --> 00:11:38.528
Wow, seriously...

00:11:38.552 --> 00:11:40.885
What would you do
without a friend like me?

00:11:42.824 --> 00:11:44.310
I told you.

00:11:44.335 --> 00:11:47.361
We have nothing to say
and we don't know anything!

00:11:47.805 --> 00:11:50.877
We can't even get
into 'It's You' right now!

00:11:52.756 --> 00:11:53.779
Reporters called again?

00:11:54.746 --> 00:11:56.206
They're really persistent.

00:11:56.741 --> 00:11:58.512
Don't answer any calls for now.

00:11:58.581 --> 00:12:00.812
Still no contact with Director Yun?

00:12:01.826 --> 00:12:04.591
Bia isn't answering my texts or calls.

00:12:05.551 --> 00:12:07.461
Did you try going to Director
Yun's house to see her?

00:12:09.412 --> 00:12:10.446
Have you

00:12:10.754 --> 00:12:11.815
contacted Yukyung?

00:12:13.722 --> 00:12:14.872
She hasn't replied to me either.

00:12:15.891 --> 00:12:19.437
An agency also claims
they are currently...

00:12:19.527 --> 00:12:20.432
Woah.

00:12:20.456 --> 00:12:22.391
These people are like leeches.

00:12:23.195 --> 00:12:25.717
Reporter, we have nothing to say!

00:12:25.811 --> 00:12:27.304
Some fans of Han Sunho--

00:12:27.328 --> 00:12:27.986
Yes?

00:12:27.987 --> 00:12:31.651
The voices criticizing It's You's
Director Yun are growing louder.

00:12:31.675 --> 00:12:32.556
Sunho.

00:12:32.702 --> 00:12:33.424
Yeah?

00:12:33.745 --> 00:12:35.586
A detective is looking for you.

00:12:37.063 --> 00:12:38.063
A detective?

00:12:40.747 --> 00:12:42.788
Thank you for your time, Mr. Han.

00:12:44.332 --> 00:12:45.816
Why is the detective looking for me?

00:12:47.131 --> 00:12:48.599
Do you know Yang Seonae?

00:12:49.385 --> 00:12:50.195
What?

00:12:51.291 --> 00:12:52.660
Why are you asking about Yang Seonae?

00:12:53.018 --> 00:12:54.892
Yang Seonae is currently missing.

00:12:55.036 --> 00:12:57.968
A missing person report was
filed from the nursing home.

00:12:58.431 --> 00:12:59.563
Missing?

00:12:59.632 --> 00:13:01.870
Do you know about the incident
where a nursing home worker

00:13:01.911 --> 00:13:03.772
took Yang Seonae out
without permission, right?

00:13:04.029 --> 00:13:05.342
You were there at the scene.

00:13:06.871 --> 00:13:08.105
Does that incident...

00:13:08.125 --> 00:13:09.633
have anything to do with
her disappearance that day?

00:13:09.700 --> 00:13:11.088
That's what I'm investigating.

00:13:11.410 --> 00:13:15.886
I heard Sul Jaehee took Yang Seonae
back to the nursing home.

00:13:16.364 --> 00:13:19.416
That day, the registered
guardian for for Yang Seonae

00:13:19.650 --> 00:13:22.387
was changed to Sul Jaehee.

00:13:23.171 --> 00:13:25.577
When I informed
Sul Jaehee that she was missing

00:13:25.632 --> 00:13:27.319
she declined police assistance.

00:13:28.548 --> 00:13:31.342
But something feels off,

00:13:31.555 --> 00:13:33.163
so I reached out to you.

00:13:34.001 --> 00:13:36.934
Do you know anything about this?

00:13:42.986 --> 00:13:44.271
Don't worry about it.

00:13:45.001 --> 00:13:46.784
Unless you want to make Bia suffer more.

00:13:51.156 --> 00:13:52.340
Where is

00:13:52.889 --> 00:13:54.231
that nursing home located?

00:13:58.229 --> 00:13:59.758
[Director Yun Bia, take responsibility...]

00:13:59.777 --> 00:14:01.018
[Is writer Han Sunho, connected
to the dummy scandal...]

00:14:04.682 --> 00:14:06.392
[Is writer Han Sunho, the main model
for the 'ForMe Version 2' prototype,]

00:14:06.412 --> 00:14:07.491
[connected to the
dummy scandal...]

00:14:19.188 --> 00:14:22.810
When the world doesn't go as you thought
or wanted, and you're upset,

00:14:24.810 --> 00:14:26.171
think of me.

00:14:33.260 --> 00:14:36.981
The article I mentioned earlier,
please have it ready by tomorrow.

00:14:49.800 --> 00:14:52.087
[Bia: The article I mentioned earlier,
please have it ready by tomorrow.]

00:14:57.566 --> 00:14:58.704
Jaehee.

00:15:00.304 --> 00:15:02.631
Could you publish an article for me?

00:15:05.821 --> 00:15:07.238
Mr. Han...

00:15:07.661 --> 00:15:09.951
he has nothing to do with this.

00:15:15.678 --> 00:15:17.094
But it's not like...

00:15:17.617 --> 00:15:18.981
he's completely unrelated.

00:15:23.608 --> 00:15:24.585
Have we

00:15:25.568 --> 00:15:26.981
changed a bit?

00:15:28.231 --> 00:15:29.692
Yeah, Yun Bia.

00:15:30.792 --> 00:15:32.141
You've changed.

00:15:36.242 --> 00:15:38.465
Bia never used to lie.

00:15:42.438 --> 00:15:44.499
If you lie,

00:15:46.355 --> 00:15:47.978
you become just like...

00:15:54.418 --> 00:15:55.851
Your mom.

00:16:44.634 --> 00:16:45.709
Jooyeon!

00:16:46.702 --> 00:16:48.118
Explain yourself to me.

00:16:48.701 --> 00:16:50.945
Are you really the one

00:16:52.154 --> 00:16:53.451
behind the doll and the CCTV?

00:16:54.231 --> 00:16:55.931
I didn't do it.

00:16:56.541 --> 00:16:58.123
Well, I did, but...

00:16:58.323 --> 00:17:00.671
I didn't mean to...

00:17:02.481 --> 00:17:04.171
What did you want to tell me?

00:17:06.481 --> 00:17:07.967
Director Yun...

00:17:08.567 --> 00:17:10.861
Please look after Director Yun well.

00:17:11.636 --> 00:17:12.322
What?

00:17:12.647 --> 00:17:15.045
And be careful

00:17:15.276 --> 00:17:16.714
of Director Sul.

00:17:25.291 --> 00:17:26.216
Yun Bia,

00:17:26.706 --> 00:17:28.111
about your mother...

00:17:36.868 --> 00:17:39.111
Yun Bia, contact me if you see this.

00:17:57.218 --> 00:17:58.280
Bia...

00:17:58.586 --> 00:17:59.582
Bia!

00:17:59.982 --> 00:18:00.982
Bia!

00:18:03.279 --> 00:18:04.797
Bia, please go inside...

00:18:04.827 --> 00:18:05.827
Let go of me.

00:18:09.261 --> 00:18:10.261
Please...

00:18:12.592 --> 00:18:13.921
Please...

00:18:14.898 --> 00:18:16.898
Please, please...

00:18:30.661 --> 00:18:33.657
[Yun Bia, contact me if you see this.]

00:18:40.391 --> 00:18:43.287
[Neulsarang Bookstore]

00:18:58.868 --> 00:18:59.971
Let me

00:19:00.653 --> 00:19:01.943
out of here.

00:19:02.581 --> 00:19:04.251
I need to go to Bia.

00:19:07.603 --> 00:19:08.804
Where do you think you're going?

00:19:10.294 --> 00:19:12.484
You liked it here so much.

00:19:16.508 --> 00:19:17.274
Here.

00:19:18.211 --> 00:19:19.563
The book you requested.

00:19:20.801 --> 00:19:22.641
Thank you so much.

00:19:22.995 --> 00:19:25.835
You've improved a lot in a short time.

00:19:26.106 --> 00:19:29.260
I never imagined

00:19:29.573 --> 00:19:31.435
I'd get to publish a book.

00:19:32.676 --> 00:19:34.899
It was a dream
I had given up on long ago...

00:19:35.504 --> 00:19:36.504
But,

00:19:37.525 --> 00:19:39.737
who is that book for?

00:19:44.028 --> 00:19:45.602
Oh? Jaehee!

00:19:47.178 --> 00:19:48.025
Ah.

00:19:48.178 --> 00:19:49.987
So you're Jaehee?

00:19:50.367 --> 00:19:51.435
Nice to meet you!

00:19:51.455 --> 00:19:54.144
I heard you're the same age
as my daughter.

00:19:54.352 --> 00:19:55.251
Right.

00:19:55.270 --> 00:19:57.482
Are you that poor lady?

00:19:57.682 --> 00:19:59.169
Taking care of her sick husband?

00:19:59.189 --> 00:20:00.410
Sul Jaehee, you!

00:20:04.794 --> 00:20:06.710
Yes, that's right.

00:20:07.263 --> 00:20:09.490
It was really tough for me,

00:20:09.509 --> 00:20:12.282
but thanks to you, I'm fine.

00:20:12.576 --> 00:20:15.271
And now I'm even publishing a book.

00:20:18.454 --> 00:20:20.311
Jaehee, why are you doing this?

00:20:20.312 --> 00:20:22.592
Let go, let go of this!

00:20:24.595 --> 00:20:25.695
No, no.

00:20:26.260 --> 00:20:27.264
I'm fine.

00:20:31.861 --> 00:20:34.451
I'll be going now.

00:20:36.711 --> 00:20:37.948
Where do you think you're running off to?

00:20:38.661 --> 00:20:40.151
Is being pitiful a privilege?

00:20:40.152 --> 00:20:42.042
Does it feel good to
seduce someone else's man?

00:20:42.043 --> 00:20:43.043
You!

00:20:44.940 --> 00:20:46.071
Oh my!

00:20:55.204 --> 00:20:57.111
You said you weren't
thinking about remarrying, Dad...

00:20:57.204 --> 00:20:58.204
Jaehee.

00:20:59.086 --> 00:21:00.484
I'm sorry, Jaehee.

00:21:00.710 --> 00:21:01.710
But

00:21:02.039 --> 00:21:05.502
I'm not involved with this woman, okay?

00:21:05.522 --> 00:21:08.952
You've been ignoring me
because you're seeing her.

00:21:08.953 --> 00:21:10.916
It's because of the book publication!

00:21:10.917 --> 00:21:13.201
Stop using the book
as an excuse, please!

00:21:13.220 --> 00:21:14.525
It's disgusting!

00:21:20.383 --> 00:21:22.239
If you meet her one more time,

00:21:24.391 --> 00:21:26.036
I'll kill her.

00:21:27.511 --> 00:21:28.939
Sul Jaehee, you!

00:21:34.692 --> 00:21:36.173
[Husband's Hospital]

00:21:37.532 --> 00:21:38.661
Yes, hello...

00:21:41.671 --> 00:21:42.512
What?

00:21:43.046 --> 00:21:44.726
Let's go, I'll take you there.

00:21:49.388 --> 00:21:51.962
Dad, don't go, okay?

00:21:52.062 --> 00:21:53.388
Don't go.

00:21:53.412 --> 00:21:54.278
Sul Jaehee!

00:21:54.298 --> 00:21:55.833
I'll talk to you when I get back!

00:21:58.033 --> 00:21:59.295
Dad!

00:22:03.606 --> 00:22:05.206
Dad...

00:22:09.606 --> 00:22:10.646
[No entry except for
authorized personnel]

00:22:10.665 --> 00:22:11.665
Charge to 200.

00:22:12.090 --> 00:22:12.936
Charging.

00:22:13.329 --> 00:22:14.329
Clear.

00:22:14.706 --> 00:22:15.592
Shock.

00:22:15.980 --> 00:22:17.081
No pulse.

00:22:17.970 --> 00:22:19.349
Charge to 200.

00:22:19.373 --> 00:22:20.096
Charging.

00:22:20.096 --> 00:22:20.991
Clear.

00:22:22.506 --> 00:22:23.506
Shock.

00:22:42.986 --> 00:22:44.008
Dad...

00:22:46.363 --> 00:22:47.064
Da...

00:22:47.368 --> 00:22:48.505
Dad!

00:22:49.326 --> 00:22:50.600
Dad!

00:22:52.867 --> 00:22:54.806
Dad, wait...

00:22:55.446 --> 00:22:56.813
Are you okay, Miss?

00:22:57.130 --> 00:22:58.794
Yang Seonae's Guardian!

00:22:59.394 --> 00:23:00.738
Are you in pain?

00:23:02.099 --> 00:23:03.180
Can you see me?

00:23:05.522 --> 00:23:06.941
Are you okay?

00:23:07.631 --> 00:23:08.985
Are you okay, Guardian?

00:23:31.288 --> 00:23:32.938
Why didn't you just die back then?

00:23:34.844 --> 00:23:36.971
Bia shouldn't be hurt anymore.

00:23:39.611 --> 00:23:41.498
Bia did nothing wrong.

00:23:42.939 --> 00:23:44.000
That's right.

00:23:45.691 --> 00:23:46.783
Bia...

00:23:47.902 --> 00:23:49.412
did nothing wrong.

00:23:52.491 --> 00:23:53.580
At first,

00:23:54.483 --> 00:23:57.113
I went to Bia to get revenge on you.

00:23:58.181 --> 00:23:59.102
But...

00:24:01.131 --> 00:24:03.320
Bia wasn't important to you.

00:24:04.971 --> 00:24:05.876
No.

00:24:06.681 --> 00:24:07.791
My daughter is...

00:24:08.984 --> 00:24:10.891
the most important thing to me.

00:24:12.001 --> 00:24:13.881
Bia would never know that.

00:24:17.471 --> 00:24:19.803
Bia was ashamed of you.

00:24:21.037 --> 00:24:22.989
She locked you away in a nursing home

00:24:23.483 --> 00:24:26.236
and created a fake mom to erase you.

00:24:26.806 --> 00:24:28.111
My Bia.

00:24:28.971 --> 00:24:30.687
I'm so sorry.

00:24:32.421 --> 00:24:33.709
If you're sorry to Bia,

00:24:34.409 --> 00:24:36.548
stop pretending to be her mom

00:24:38.089 --> 00:24:39.431
and disappear from her life.

00:24:42.807 --> 00:24:45.278
Bia is happy when she's with me,

00:24:46.378 --> 00:24:47.717
but there's something else

00:24:48.587 --> 00:24:50.331
bothering me besides you.

00:24:57.664 --> 00:24:59.526
Let's meet tomorrow and talk.

00:25:06.056 --> 00:25:09.112
['It's You' Director Yun Bia turns her
still-living mother into an AI]

00:25:09.131 --> 00:25:11.287
Is it right to publish
the article like this?

00:25:11.459 --> 00:25:12.195
Really?

00:25:12.215 --> 00:25:14.484
Did Director Sul really order this?

00:25:14.564 --> 00:25:16.040
Are you sure you heard correctly, Yukyung?

00:25:16.060 --> 00:25:18.288
Even if Director Yun ordered it,

00:25:18.519 --> 00:25:22.192
Director Sul would stop it,
not execute it.

00:25:23.359 --> 00:25:24.260
I don't know, I don't know.

00:25:24.287 --> 00:25:26.102
I can't do this, so you do it, San.

00:25:26.136 --> 00:25:26.883
What?

00:25:27.111 --> 00:25:28.625
I'm in charge of development.

00:25:29.481 --> 00:25:30.747
Kyungtae should do it.

00:25:30.767 --> 00:25:31.788
I can't do it, I can't.

00:25:31.808 --> 00:25:33.484
You know I'm shy.

00:25:33.930 --> 00:25:35.692
How can I talk to a reporter?

00:25:35.732 --> 00:25:36.379
What?

00:25:36.620 --> 00:25:38.468
You drink with reporters all the time,
Kyungtae!

00:25:38.488 --> 00:25:40.404
I drink with them,
but I can't talk to them!

00:25:40.904 --> 00:25:42.146
I don't know, I don't know.

00:25:42.166 --> 00:25:43.406
I don't want to do this!

00:25:43.426 --> 00:25:44.087
I really can't do it!

00:25:44.107 --> 00:25:45.862
I can't do this!

00:25:56.107 --> 00:25:57.004
Director Sul,

00:25:57.136 --> 00:25:58.628
are you really going to
publish this article?

00:25:58.708 --> 00:26:01.544
Our company's reputation isn't
great right now.

00:26:01.739 --> 00:26:03.684
Director Yun must have a plan.

00:26:04.961 --> 00:26:07.122
Don't you know about
facing things head-on?

00:26:11.555 --> 00:26:12.622
Mr. Han!

00:26:22.061 --> 00:26:25.822
If you wanted to see me this early,
I hope you have a good reason.

00:26:26.615 --> 00:26:27.670
Why did you do it?

00:26:27.792 --> 00:26:28.604
Do what?

00:26:29.226 --> 00:26:31.537
The things you had Jooyeon
do to keep me away from Bia.

00:26:34.818 --> 00:26:35.772
Did she say that?

00:26:39.234 --> 00:26:40.724
Do you believe that?

00:26:43.584 --> 00:26:46.202
You're more naive than I thought,
Han Sunho.

00:26:51.335 --> 00:26:52.308
She...

00:26:53.522 --> 00:26:55.044
loved Bia.

00:26:56.430 --> 00:26:58.128
She was jealous of you, Han Sunho.

00:26:58.398 --> 00:27:00.030
That's why she did those things.

00:27:01.887 --> 00:27:02.935
Jealousy...

00:27:03.832 --> 00:27:06.484
I'll bind you and keep you
by my side forever.

00:27:07.705 --> 00:27:09.576
If I take everything you have,

00:27:10.776 --> 00:27:12.231
you'll belong to me too.

00:27:13.311 --> 00:27:14.712
That's a twisted love

00:27:15.872 --> 00:27:17.351
that's gone too far.

00:27:22.393 --> 00:27:24.171
Why did you make her like that?

00:27:24.908 --> 00:27:25.621
What?

00:27:25.781 --> 00:27:26.781
Do you know...

00:27:27.951 --> 00:27:30.493
Bia's unhappiness started

00:27:31.165 --> 00:27:34.398
the day you took her hand and ran?

00:27:35.501 --> 00:27:36.886
Think about it.

00:27:37.771 --> 00:27:39.633
When did problems start

00:27:39.816 --> 00:27:42.541
for 'It's You' and Bia?

00:27:43.891 --> 00:27:45.298
Did you really

00:27:45.555 --> 00:27:47.548
drop Yang Seonae off
at the nursing home

00:27:48.692 --> 00:27:49.620
that day?

00:27:52.181 --> 00:27:53.396
Yang Seonae

00:27:53.770 --> 00:27:54.891
is missing.

00:27:54.901 --> 00:27:55.973
Missing?

00:27:57.361 --> 00:27:58.791
Don't tell Bia.

00:27:58.961 --> 00:28:00.331
I'll find out what's going on.

00:28:02.821 --> 00:28:06.102
Bia had to hide her mom,
even from her best friend.

00:28:06.576 --> 00:28:07.985
You know what will happen

00:28:09.069 --> 00:28:10.627
if Bia finds out her
mom is missing, right?

00:28:17.777 --> 00:28:18.708
And

00:28:20.134 --> 00:28:23.581
if you don't want to make Bia
more unhappy, stop caring about her.

00:28:24.111 --> 00:28:26.561
I'll make Bia happy.

00:28:32.829 --> 00:28:34.971
Just one hour of happiness.

00:28:35.171 --> 00:28:35.965
Just?

00:28:36.392 --> 00:28:39.837
Do you know how happy
Bia was during that hour?

00:28:40.245 --> 00:28:43.491
Without thinking about
her painful past or uncertain future,

00:28:43.492 --> 00:28:44.708
Bia was just happy.

00:28:44.791 --> 00:28:46.173
Perfectly happy!

00:28:47.173 --> 00:28:48.905
And you ruined it.

00:28:49.011 --> 00:28:49.826
But, what?

00:28:50.625 --> 00:28:51.625
Just?

00:28:52.161 --> 00:28:53.053
Are you sure

00:28:53.809 --> 00:28:55.388
Bia was happy?

00:28:56.568 --> 00:28:57.707
Someone once said,

00:28:58.071 --> 00:29:00.133
there's a fine line between
understanding and misunderstanding.

00:29:00.333 --> 00:29:01.581
Don't be mistaken.

00:29:02.161 --> 00:29:04.234
Yun Bia was always a free spirit.

00:29:05.591 --> 00:29:07.297
Neither you nor I...

00:29:08.097 --> 00:29:10.507
made Bia happy.

00:29:12.230 --> 00:29:14.206
It's us who want to
be happy through Bia,

00:29:15.430 --> 00:29:17.901
because we want
to be by her side.

00:29:33.056 --> 00:29:33.738
[Detective Kim Kanho]

00:29:33.757 --> 00:29:35.678
Sending the address as requested.

00:29:49.918 --> 00:29:50.713
Bia,

00:29:53.483 --> 00:29:54.484
are you feeling better?

00:29:54.665 --> 00:29:55.512
Oh.

00:29:55.951 --> 00:29:56.893
You're here?

00:30:01.948 --> 00:30:04.671
I knew it
since you weren't eating properly.

00:30:05.714 --> 00:30:07.377
Come on, eat your porridge
and take your medicine.

00:30:08.431 --> 00:30:10.220
Jaehee, did you release the article?

00:30:15.471 --> 00:30:16.506
Yun Bia.

00:30:21.624 --> 00:30:23.099
Do you really like him?

00:30:26.821 --> 00:30:29.191
Focus on taking care of yourself first.

00:30:38.804 --> 00:30:42.118
[Dolbom Nursing Home]

00:30:56.702 --> 00:30:58.641
Did the guardian really say to
throw everything away?

00:30:59.341 --> 00:31:02.472
Yes, the new guardian
instructed us to do so.

00:31:02.832 --> 00:31:03.874
Was that person

00:31:04.286 --> 00:31:05.516
Sul Jaehee?

00:31:08.210 --> 00:31:09.612
Yes, that's correct.

00:31:10.441 --> 00:31:11.511
This way, please.

00:31:25.485 --> 00:31:28.044
Just in case, we kept the belongings.

00:31:28.961 --> 00:31:31.074
These were things stuck on the wall

00:31:31.129 --> 00:31:33.269
I don't know what it means, but

00:31:33.456 --> 00:31:36.436
Yang Seonae kept writing
the same thing over and over.

00:31:36.855 --> 00:31:38.014
This is a book passage.

00:31:38.401 --> 00:31:39.088
What?

00:31:43.575 --> 00:31:44.489
Can I

00:31:44.884 --> 00:31:46.588
deliver these belongings instead?

00:31:52.688 --> 00:31:53.529
San.

00:31:53.553 --> 00:31:54.043
Yes?

00:31:54.063 --> 00:31:56.227
The Directors aren't at the office,
and we're all down.

00:31:56.228 --> 00:32:00.041
How about we grab
a refreshing beer nearby?

00:32:00.741 --> 00:32:03.092
I can't, I just got off suspension.

00:32:07.188 --> 00:32:08.037
Yukyung.

00:32:08.092 --> 00:32:08.797
Yes?

00:32:08.821 --> 00:32:10.046
Did you submit the article?

00:32:11.509 --> 00:32:12.509
Well...

00:32:13.121 --> 00:32:13.897
Yes!

00:32:14.657 --> 00:32:15.444
Yes...

00:32:16.482 --> 00:32:17.721
You didn't submit the article.

00:32:17.914 --> 00:32:18.734
Geez.

00:32:20.426 --> 00:32:22.445
I really can't do it!

00:32:22.446 --> 00:32:24.240
Why do I have to do this?

00:32:24.314 --> 00:32:25.415
Well,

00:32:25.476 --> 00:32:28.896
because Director Sul specifically
asked you to submit it.

00:32:29.466 --> 00:32:32.402
But why me?

00:32:33.366 --> 00:32:34.791
I really don't get it.

00:32:35.006 --> 00:32:37.620
What will I do if our company goes under?

00:32:53.597 --> 00:32:55.579
[If I were your tomorrow]

00:33:00.431 --> 00:33:02.298
[My Little Paradise]

00:33:02.318 --> 00:33:03.620
A publication?

00:33:06.355 --> 00:33:07.355
Wow.

00:33:07.741 --> 00:33:09.371
So, have you finally become an writer?

00:33:11.155 --> 00:33:13.017
What do you mean a writer...

00:33:15.083 --> 00:33:17.466
I'm an writer, yes, a writer!

00:33:17.646 --> 00:33:18.681
Writer Yang.

00:33:21.401 --> 00:33:22.601
Congratulations!

00:33:23.491 --> 00:33:24.367
I'm jealous.

00:33:24.966 --> 00:33:28.746
Sunho will become
a much more amazing author than me.

00:33:29.165 --> 00:33:31.701
So, can I finally
read the book you wrote?

00:33:31.862 --> 00:33:33.423
I'll make sure to save
a copy for you, Sunho.

00:33:33.570 --> 00:33:34.763
Awesome!

00:33:35.063 --> 00:33:36.799
I've been so curious about the content.

00:33:38.068 --> 00:33:40.129
It's just a typical love story.

00:33:41.401 --> 00:33:42.766
Is it a romance genre?

00:33:43.546 --> 00:33:44.335
Yeah.

00:33:46.076 --> 00:33:47.076
Ah...

00:33:48.101 --> 00:33:49.659
Is the book about your husband?

00:33:49.745 --> 00:33:50.693
No.

00:33:51.088 --> 00:33:52.515
You said it back then.

00:33:53.166 --> 00:33:55.696
You wrote it while thinking of someone.

00:33:56.531 --> 00:33:57.587
There is someone.

00:33:58.481 --> 00:34:00.051
My last love.

00:34:04.804 --> 00:34:08.111
Let's meet in front of the
Neulsarang Bookstore next Friday.

00:34:21.321 --> 00:34:22.507
Um...

00:34:23.307 --> 00:34:24.896
Han Sunho?

00:34:24.989 --> 00:34:25.762
Oh.

00:34:25.875 --> 00:34:26.875
Yes.

00:34:28.526 --> 00:34:30.636
Someone asked me to give this to you.

00:34:31.761 --> 00:34:33.069
[My Little Paradise]

00:34:39.022 --> 00:34:41.718
[My Little Paradise]

00:34:48.428 --> 00:34:51.988
"She ran and ran
wherever her feet took her."

00:34:52.801 --> 00:34:55.092
"Until the darkness could
no longer chase her."

00:34:56.051 --> 00:34:59.551
It seemed like
there was light far ahead.

00:35:00.701 --> 00:35:01.989
If she went there.

00:35:02.489 --> 00:35:03.815
If she reached that place

00:35:03.835 --> 00:35:07.912
there would be a paradise
to save her from misery.

00:35:08.896 --> 00:35:11.113
But when she arrived
after running so hard

00:35:11.430 --> 00:35:13.106
there was nothing there.

00:35:13.656 --> 00:35:14.966
Nothing at all.

00:35:16.111 --> 00:35:17.793
Only then did she realize.

00:35:17.855 --> 00:35:19.781
"Only then did she realize."

00:35:25.493 --> 00:35:26.763
"Hidden within the
darkness she fled from,"

00:35:27.275 --> 00:35:29.273
"wanting so desperately to escape,"

00:35:30.073 --> 00:35:33.191
"was the paradise she dreamed
of all along."

00:35:42.046 --> 00:35:43.980
[My Little Paradise]

00:35:44.000 --> 00:35:46.809
[To Writer Sunho. With Love.]

00:35:49.946 --> 00:35:51.494
[A very small but happy
paradise of her own.]

00:35:55.992 --> 00:35:58.141
[A very small but happy
paradise of her own.]

00:35:59.370 --> 00:36:00.841
"A very small, but."

00:36:01.561 --> 00:36:03.714
A very small but happy

00:36:04.559 --> 00:36:06.931
paradise of her own.

00:36:17.400 --> 00:36:18.776
What are you doing up so late?

00:36:19.076 --> 00:36:20.289
Have you seen my car keys?

00:36:24.406 --> 00:36:25.321
Here are your keys.

00:36:26.181 --> 00:36:27.010
Thank you.

00:36:28.431 --> 00:36:30.684
Hey, where are you off to now?

00:36:46.741 --> 00:36:47.783
Are you okay?

00:36:51.581 --> 00:36:53.129
Han Sunho,

00:36:53.392 --> 00:36:54.483
why are you here?

00:36:55.231 --> 00:36:57.620
Why are you dressed
so lightly in the cold?

00:36:57.968 --> 00:36:59.195
Are you eating well?

00:36:59.691 --> 00:37:01.441
Sleeping well?

00:37:04.716 --> 00:37:06.742
Did you come all this way just to
ask me something that small?

00:37:07.607 --> 00:37:08.898
It's not small.

00:37:09.091 --> 00:37:11.701
It's the most
important thing to me.

00:37:12.056 --> 00:37:13.616
If you're done, please leave.

00:37:19.524 --> 00:37:20.603
Take this.

00:37:21.401 --> 00:37:22.805
What's this?

00:37:23.084 --> 00:37:24.596
It's Yang Seonae's belongings.

00:37:24.966 --> 00:37:26.302
They belong to your mother.

00:37:26.475 --> 00:37:27.475
[My Little Paradise]

00:37:30.084 --> 00:37:30.833
Why...

00:37:31.862 --> 00:37:33.596
Why do you have this?

00:37:34.133 --> 00:37:35.352
I once told you

00:37:35.860 --> 00:37:37.893
that someone helped
me come out of hiding.

00:37:39.109 --> 00:37:42.378
The person who helped me
step out into the world...

00:37:44.111 --> 00:37:45.581
was Aunt Seonae.

00:37:52.533 --> 00:37:54.083
That woman is not my mother.

00:37:56.201 --> 00:37:57.393
My mother is dead.

00:37:57.471 --> 00:37:59.395
But she's your only family, Bia.

00:37:59.417 --> 00:38:00.390
Family?

00:38:03.048 --> 00:38:05.008
A woman who leaves
her husband and daughter

00:38:05.508 --> 00:38:08.324
to have an affair with another man,
is she still considered family?

00:38:08.431 --> 00:38:11.615
Maybe it would've been better
if my mom had died in that accident.

00:38:11.635 --> 00:38:12.688
So,

00:38:13.024 --> 00:38:16.435
don't try to lecture me
when you don't even know.

00:38:17.565 --> 00:38:19.405
My only family is Jaehee,

00:38:20.862 --> 00:38:22.295
who's always been with me.

00:38:27.047 --> 00:38:28.624
Jaehee didn't stay with you,

00:38:30.011 --> 00:38:31.187
she trapped you.

00:38:31.899 --> 00:38:34.425
Han Sunho, you're mistaken.

00:38:35.466 --> 00:38:36.305
Do you

00:38:37.035 --> 00:38:38.147
know me well?

00:38:38.206 --> 00:38:41.103
What do you know about me
to keep interfering in my life?

00:38:41.906 --> 00:38:43.092
Take this back.

00:38:44.251 --> 00:38:45.421
Throw it away if you want.

00:38:48.191 --> 00:38:49.261
And,

00:38:51.943 --> 00:38:53.901
don't get involved again.

00:38:56.981 --> 00:38:58.447
Why are you running away?

00:39:00.371 --> 00:39:02.141
Why are you trapping yourself again?

00:39:03.131 --> 00:39:04.941
Being alone until now,

00:39:05.546 --> 00:39:07.270
and wanting to be alone again,

00:39:08.370 --> 00:39:10.121
it's all because of Jaehee.

00:39:10.851 --> 00:39:13.052
It's not Jaehee
making me alone again,

00:39:13.509 --> 00:39:15.091
it's you.

00:39:15.581 --> 00:39:17.764
If I hadn't known what
it felt like to be together,

00:39:18.713 --> 00:39:20.296
it would have been better.

00:39:21.401 --> 00:39:23.405
You said I could be okay, right?

00:39:24.871 --> 00:39:25.728
No.

00:39:27.453 --> 00:39:29.307
Sunho, you're wrong.

00:39:30.431 --> 00:39:31.841
Look at me now.

00:39:36.872 --> 00:39:37.640
Just...

00:39:39.033 --> 00:39:40.209
read this.

00:39:43.692 --> 00:39:48.318
[My Little Paradise]

00:40:05.333 --> 00:40:06.890
Jaehee didn't stay with you

00:40:08.263 --> 00:40:09.563
she trapped you.

00:40:11.381 --> 00:40:12.816
Why are you running away?

00:40:14.211 --> 00:40:16.031
Why are you trapping yourself again?

00:40:21.571 --> 00:40:23.954
[My Little Paradise]

00:40:34.408 --> 00:40:39.504
She ran and ran
wherever her feet took her.

00:40:40.341 --> 00:40:43.291
Until the darkness could
no longer follow her.

00:40:44.431 --> 00:40:47.911
It seemed like she saw a light far ahead.

00:40:50.501 --> 00:40:51.851
If she went there.

00:40:52.241 --> 00:40:53.686
If she reached that place

00:40:53.687 --> 00:40:57.701
there would be a paradise
to save her from misery.

00:41:00.271 --> 00:41:02.381
But when she arrived
after running so hard

00:41:02.856 --> 00:41:04.473
there was nothing there.

00:41:05.066 --> 00:41:06.356
Nothing at all.

00:41:09.411 --> 00:41:11.596
Only then did she realize.

00:41:12.761 --> 00:41:14.124
Hidden within the
darkness she fled from,

00:41:14.524 --> 00:41:17.688
wanting so desperately to escape,

00:41:18.551 --> 00:41:21.701
was the paradise she
dreamed of all along.

00:41:24.531 --> 00:41:26.866
A very small but happy

00:41:27.529 --> 00:41:29.492
paradise of her own.

00:41:47.238 --> 00:41:49.822
Detective, I'll give you an address.

00:41:49.841 --> 00:41:51.227
Could you come over?

00:41:51.651 --> 00:41:52.651
Maybe...

00:41:52.721 --> 00:41:54.824
Yang Seonae might be there.

00:42:28.528 --> 00:42:29.772
Aunt!

00:42:33.038 --> 00:42:33.943
Aunt!

00:42:35.976 --> 00:42:37.211
Aunt Seonae!

00:42:45.210 --> 00:42:46.411
Aunt!

00:42:57.259 --> 00:42:59.412
[Neulsarang Bookstore]

00:43:28.730 --> 00:43:29.730
Aunt!

00:43:30.491 --> 00:43:31.508
Aunt Seonae!

00:43:31.643 --> 00:43:32.841
It's Sunho.

00:43:33.531 --> 00:43:35.041
Aunt, wake up!

00:43:36.099 --> 00:43:37.299
Bia...

00:43:38.211 --> 00:43:39.311
Aunt!

00:43:45.224 --> 00:43:47.156
Aunt, wake up!

00:44:03.586 --> 00:44:05.231
Aunt!